Class ImageProcessParam

    • com.example.ARmirrorS.Server.Constants.ImageProcessParam

    Class ImageProcessParam

    Class ImageProcessParam defines the Background extraction algorithm selected by the user from the server side.

    Since:
    2019-12-05
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Yussuf Khalil, Daniel King, ykhalil2@illinois.edu, dking32@illinois.edu
